description:
This is a special &quot;embedded subtitles&quot; version of the Russian sci-fi classic, Petlya Oriona a.k.a. Orion's Loop (1981) compatible with Google Chromecast. Optimized file size is small but it is the same quality as much bigger (and older) RIPs. 

Audio track language is Russian. English subtitles are hard-embedded on screen.

Google Chromecast supports just a limited number of video and audio codecs and container file types. Chromecast still does not handle subtitles, so the English subtitles have been overlayed directly on the video image with this download.

Video: H264 ( 720 x 544 ) --- Audio: AAC (m4a) stereo 48000

This movie file with embedded subtitles was created using VLC and Avanti.
